Package: GRANBase
Type: Package
Title: Creating continuously integrated package repositories
Version: 1.0.1
Author: Gabriel Becker[aut,cre], Cory Barr [cre,ctb]
Maintainer: Gabriel Becker <becker.gabriel@gene.com>
Copyright: Genentech Inc
Description: Repository based tools for department and analysis level
    reproduciblity. 'GRANBase' allows creation of custom branched,
    continuous integration-ready R repositories, including incremental testing of only packages which have changed since the last repository build.
    package versions.
